    • hasMorePackets

      public boolean hasMorePackets()
      Test if more packets can be generated.
      Specified by:
      hasMorePackets in interface PacketGenerator
      Returns:
      true if more packets must be generated and false otherwise.

      This occurs if either numPkts < 0 (infinite number of packets) or numPkts > 0 (limit not reached).
